      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, delivering power through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been proactively addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis is tightened with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While showing honest cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral, analog driving experience for the serious enthusiast.",
